# <type>[optional scope]: <description>
# 
# [optional body]
# 
# [optional footer(s)]
# 
# 类型 (Types):
#   feat:     新功能
#   fix:      修复bug
#   docs:     文档更新
#   style:    代码格式化
#   refactor: 代码重构
#   test:     测试相关
#   chore:    构建/工具相关
#   perf:     性能优化
#   ci:       CI/CD相关
#   build:    构建系统
#   revert:   回滚提交
# 
# 作用域 (Scopes):
#   api, auth, db, docker, config, middleware, model, service, 
#   handler, test, ci, docs, user, post, server, client, utils, deps
# 
# 示例:
#   feat(auth): add JWT token validation
#   fix(db): resolve connection timeout issue
#   docs(readme): update installation guide
#   refactor(api): simplify error handling logic
# 
# 规则:
#   - 使用现在时态: "add" 不是 "added"
#   - 首字母小写
#   - 描述不超过50个字符
#   - 正文每行不超过72个字符